{
  "stem": "26142.11",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And of course I was illegal, so they had to share.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And those rations weren't-- weren't too, too generous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So they had to share it with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I used to see-- the house was ran by one of the daughters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "When the mother was away, it was ran like a factory-- around the clock, the table-- there was was plenty of order on the table with white napkins and white tablecloth.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But when I looked at the food that was put up on the table, I used to think to myself, maybe that would be enough for me, maybe.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I decided, in that case, I won't even-- I, I won't even finish what I'm-- what I'm getting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that's how de-- not dehydrated-- I was so hungry from those four, five months not having a decent meal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this, I talk about it because it was important to me at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I mana-- I managed to, to overcome-- to overcome that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same thing happened to my brother the-- in the other place-- not as bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fortunately, in deep side in Hungary, in a city of Mariapocs, there was a cousin of ours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name, Sanyi Fixler-- he passed away a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- passed away in Miami Beach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had a mom and pop store in that city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's-- it was-- it wasn't a city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the area where that Mariapocs is is called [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nyiregyhaza ?] in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is the bras-- breadbasket of, of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From that area, they supplied bread for the entire German army during the wartime.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but the people over there, they had no rationing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
